        <span style="font-family:方正仿宋_GBK; font-size:16pt">对聘用人员实行岗位管理和绩效工资制度。</span>
    </p>
    <p style="line-height:32pt; margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-indent:24pt; widows:0">
        <span style="font-family:方正仿宋_GBK; font-size:16pt">幼儿园实行教职工双向聘任机制，以实现人力资源的优化组合，尽可能让每一位教职工找到适合自己的岗位。园长通过园长办公会、教代会、园务委员会，</span>
        <span style="font-family:方正仿宋_GBK; font-size:16pt">根据编制部门核定的编制数额、岗位数和岗位任职条件及教育行政部门、幼儿园相关规定</span>
        <span style="font-family:方正仿宋_GBK; font-size:16pt">确定岗位设置及职位数并通过聘任方案。教职工实行双向选择，园长及无相应聘任权的干部不得干预聘任过程和聘任结果。</span>
    </p>
    <p style="line-height:32pt; margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-indent:24pt; widows:0">
        <span style="font-family:方正仿宋_GBK; font-size:16pt">新任干部由园长提名、党支部组织考察、民意测评满意度超过80%，园务委员会审议通过，方可聘任</span>
        <span style="font-family:方正仿宋_GBK; font-size:16pt">。</span>
    </p>
    <p style="line-height:32pt; margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-indent:24pt; widows:0">
        <span style="font-family:方正仿宋_GBK; font-size:16pt">新入职教职工的聘任必须严格按照幼儿园招聘方案执行</span>
        <span style="font-family:方正仿宋_GBK; font-size:16pt">，</span>
        <span style="font-family:方正仿宋_GBK; font-size:16pt">坚持公开、公正</span>
        <span style="font-family:方正仿宋_GBK; font-size:16pt">的</span>
        <span style="font-family:方正仿宋_GBK; font-size:16pt">原则</span>
        <span style="font-family:方正仿宋_GBK; font-size:16pt">。</span>
    </p>
    <p style="line-height:32pt; margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-indent:24pt; widows:0">
        <span style="font-family:方正仿宋_GBK; font-size:16pt; font-weight:bold">第3</span>
        <span style="font-family:方正仿宋_GBK; font-size:16pt; font-weight:bold">4</span>
        <span style="font-family:方正仿宋_GBK; font-size:16pt; font-weight:bold">条</span>
        <span style="font-family:方正仿宋_GBK; font-size:16pt"> 本园</span>
        <span style="font-family:方正仿宋_GBK; font-size:16pt">教职工享有下列权利：</span>
    </p>
    <p style="line-height:32pt; margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-indent:24pt; widows:0">
        <span style="font-family:方正仿宋_GBK; font-size:16pt">1. </span>
        <span style="font-family:方正仿宋_GBK; font-size:16pt">开展教育教学活动</span>
        <span style="font-family:方正仿宋_GBK; font-size:16pt">，</span>
        <span style="font-family:方正仿宋_GBK; font-size:16pt">从事教育教学改革和实验；</span>
    </p>
    <p style="line-height:32pt; margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-indent:24pt; widows:0">
        <span style="font-family:方正仿宋_GBK; font-size:16pt">2.</span>
        <span style="font-family:方正仿宋_GBK; font-size:16pt">参加教育教学科研、学术交流</span>
        <span style="font-family:方正仿宋_GBK; font-size:16pt">，</span>
        <span style="font-family:方正仿宋_GBK; font-size:16pt">加入专业学术团体</span>
        <span style="font-family:方正仿宋_GBK; font-size:16pt">，</span>
        <span style="font-family:方正仿宋_GBK; font-size:16pt">在学术活动中充分发表意见；</span>
    </p>
    <p style="line-height:32pt; margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-indent:24pt; widows:0">
        <span style="font-family:方正仿宋_GBK; font-size:16pt">3.</span>
        <span style="font-family:方正仿宋_GBK; font-size:16pt">关注与</span>
        <span style="font-family:方正仿宋_GBK; font-size:16pt">指导幼儿学习和发展，指导家长科学育儿。</span>
    </p>
    <p style="line-height:32pt; margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-indent:24pt; widows:0">
        <span style="font-family:方正仿宋_GBK; font-size:16pt">4.</span>
        <span style="font-family:方正仿宋_GBK; font-size:16pt">按时获取工资报酬</span>
        <span style="font-family:方正仿宋_GBK; font-size:16pt">，</span>
        <span style="font-family:方正仿宋_GBK; font-size:16pt">享受国家规定的福利待遇以及寒暑假的带薪休假；</span>
    </p>
    <p style="line-height:32pt; margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-indent:24pt; widows:0">
        <span style="font-family:方正仿宋_GBK; font-size:16pt">5.</span>
        <span style="font-family:方正仿宋_GBK; font-size:16pt">通过教职工代表大会或其他形式参与学校管理</span>
        <span style="font-family:方正仿宋_GBK; font-size:16pt">，</span>
        <span style="font-family:方正仿宋_GBK; font-size:16pt">对学校工作提出意见和建议；对学校重大事项有知情权；对不公正待遇或处分有申诉权；</span>
    </p>
    <p style="line-height:32pt; margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-indent:24pt; widows:0">
        <span style="font-family:方正仿宋_GBK; font-size:16pt">6.</span>
        <span style="font-family:方正仿宋_GBK; font-size:16pt">使用学校设施设备、图书音像资料及其他教育教学用品；</span>
    </p>
    <p style="line-height:32pt; margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-indent:24pt; widows:0">
        <span style="font-family:方正仿宋_GBK; font-size:16pt">7.</span>
        <span style="font-family:方正仿宋_GBK; font-size:16pt">参加进修或者其他方式的培训；</span>
    </p>
    <p style="line-height:32pt; margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-indent:24pt; widows:0">
        <span style="font-family:方正仿宋_GBK; font-size:16pt">8.法律法规规定的其他权利。</span>
    </p>
    <p style="line-height:32pt; margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-indent:24pt; widows:0">
        <span style="font-family:方正仿宋_GBK; font-size:16pt; font-weight:bold">第3</span>
        <span style="font-family:方正仿宋_GBK; font-size:16pt; font-weight:bold">5</span>
        <span style="font-family:方正仿宋_GBK; font-size:16pt; font-weight:bold">条</span>
        <span style="font-family:方正仿宋_GBK; font-size:16pt"> 本园</span>
        <span style="font-family:方正仿宋_GBK; font-size:16pt">教职工应当履行下列义务:</span>
    </p>
    <p style="line-height:32pt; margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-indent:24pt; widows:0">
        <span style="font-family:方正仿宋_GBK; font-size:16pt">1.</span>
        <span style="font-family:方正仿宋_GBK; font-size:16pt">遵守法律法规、职业道德规范、学校章程及规章制度</span>
        <span style="font-family:方正仿宋_GBK; font-size:16pt">，</span>
        <span style="font-family:方正仿宋_GBK; font-size:16pt">为人师表</span>
        <span style="font-family:方正仿宋_GBK; font-size:16pt">，</span>
        <span style="font-family:方正仿宋_GBK; font-size:16pt">忠诚于人民教育事业；</span>
    </p>
    <p style="line-height:32pt; margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-indent:24pt; widows:0">
        <span style="font-family:方正仿宋_GBK; font-size:16pt">2.</span>
        <span style="font-family:方正仿宋_GBK; font-size:16pt">贯彻国家教育方针</span>
        <span style="font-family:方正仿宋_GBK; font-size:16pt">，</span>
        <span style="font-family:方正仿宋_GBK; font-size:16pt">执行幼儿园工作计划</span>
        <span style="font-family:方正仿宋_GBK; font-size:16pt">，</span>
        <span style="font-family:方正仿宋_GBK; font-size:16pt">履行教师聘约和岗位职责</span>
        <span style="font-family:方正仿宋_GBK; font-size:16pt">，</span>
        <span style="font-family:方正仿宋_GBK; font-size:16pt">完成教育教学工作任务；</span>
    </p>
    <p style="line-height:32pt; margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-indent:24pt; widows:0">
        <span style="font-family:方正仿宋_GBK; font-size:16pt">3.</span>
        <span style="font-family:方正仿宋_GBK; font-size:16pt">弘扬爰心与责任感</span>
        <span style="font-family:方正仿宋_GBK; font-size:16pt">，</span>
        <span style="font-family:方正仿宋_GBK; font-size:16pt">关心、爰护全体幼儿</span>
        <span style="font-family:方正仿宋_GBK; font-size:16pt">，</span>
        <span style="font-family:方正仿宋_GBK; font-size:16pt">尊重幼儿人格</span>
        <span style="font-family:方正仿宋_GBK; font-size:16pt">，</span>
        <span style="font-family:方正仿宋_GBK; font-size:16pt">促进幼儿在体、智、德、美等方面的全面发展；</span>
    </p>
    <p style="line-height:32pt; margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-indent:24pt; widows:0">
        <span style="font-family:方正仿宋_GBK; font-size:16pt">4.</span>
        <span style="font-family:方正仿宋_GBK; font-size:16pt">制止有害于幼儿的行为或者其他侵犯幼儿合法权利的行为</span>
        <span style="font-family:方正仿宋_GBK; font-size:16pt">，</span>
        <span style="font-family:方正仿宋_GBK; font-size:16pt">批评和抵制有害于幼儿健康成长的现象；</span>
    </p>
    <p style="line-height:32pt; margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-indent:24pt; widows:0">
        <span style="font-family:方正仿宋_GBK; font-size:16pt">5.</span>
        <span style="font-family:方正仿宋_GBK; font-size:16pt">践行以幼儿为本理念</span>
        <span style="font-family:方正仿宋_GBK; font-size:16pt">，</span>
        <span style="font-family:方正仿宋_GBK; font-size:16pt">终身学习</span>
        <span style="font-family:方正仿宋_GBK; font-size:16pt">，</span>
        <span style="font-family:方正仿宋_GBK; font-size:16pt">与时倶进</span>
        <span style="font-family:方正仿宋_GBK; font-size:16pt">，</span>
        <span style="font-family:方正仿宋_GBK; font-size:16pt">不断提升育人水平。</span>
    </p>
    <p style="line-height:32pt; margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-indent:24pt; widows:0">
        <span style="font-family:方正仿宋_GBK; font-size:16pt">6.全体教职工须向园方提交“师德承诺书”，在工作过程中坚</span>
        <span style="font-family:方正仿宋_GBK; font-size:16pt">守承诺，绝不触碰师德红线。</span>
    </p>
    <p style="line-height:32pt; margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-indent:24pt; widows:0">
        <span style="font-family:方正仿宋_GBK; font-size:16pt">7. 幼儿园全体教职工实行一岗双责，签订 “ 安全承诺书”和“岗位责任认可书”，明确岗位工作职责和安全。</span>
    </p>
    <p style="line-height:32pt; margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-indent:24pt; widows:0">
        <span style="font-family:方正仿宋_GBK; font-size:16pt; font-weight:bold">第3</span>
        <span style="font-family:方正仿宋_GBK; font-size:16pt; font-weight:bold">6</span>
        <span style="font-family:方正仿宋_GBK; font-size:16pt; font-weight:bold">条</span>
        <span style="font-family:方正仿宋_GBK; font-size:16pt"> </span>
        <span style="font-family:方正仿宋_GBK; font-size:16pt">幼儿园施行专业发展考核和绩效考核双考核制度。考核结果作为续聘或者解聘、奖励或者处分的依据。</span>
    </p>
    <p style="line-height:32pt; margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-indent:24pt; widows:0">
        <span style="font-family:方正仿宋_GBK; font-size:16pt">幼儿园建立教职工是的档案，将师德表现作为教师考核、职务评聘、进修深造和评优先等的首要内容。对于违反师德的教师，实行一票否决制。</span>
    </p>
    <p style="line-height:32pt; margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-indent:24pt; widows:0">
        <span style="font-family:方正仿宋_GBK; font-size:16pt; font-weight:bold">第3</span>
        <span style="font-family:方正仿宋_GBK; font-size:16pt; font-weight:bold">7</span>
        <span style="font-family:方正仿宋_GBK; font-size:16pt; font-weight:bold">条</span>
        <span style="font-family:方正仿宋_GBK; font-size:16pt"> </span>
        <span style="font-family:方正仿宋_GBK; font-size:16pt">本园建立健全教职工的权利保护机制，维护教职工合法权益。</span>
    </p>
    <p style="line-height:32pt; margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-indent:24pt; widows:0">
        <span style="font-family:方正仿宋_GBK; font-size:16pt">1.幼儿园坚持按劳分配、按岗取酬、绩优酬高、薪随岗变的分配原则。</span>
    </p>
    <p style="line-height:32pt; margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-indent:24pt; widows:0">
        <span style="font-family:方正仿宋_GBK; font-size:16pt">2.聘请具备相应律师资格的人员作为幼儿园的法律顾问，以《华阳幼儿园园规》、《成都市中小学教师职业道德规范》等法律法规规范教师的职业行为，保障幼儿的合法权益；以《中华人民共和国劳动合同法》、《中华人民共和国教师法》</span>
        <span style="font-family:方正仿宋_GBK; font-size:16pt">等保障教职工的合法权益。</span>
    </p>
    <p style="line-height:32pt; margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-indent:24pt; widows:0">
        <span style="font-family:方正仿宋_GBK; font-size:16pt">3.幼儿园建立健全劳动人事争议调解委员会制度。</span>
    </p>
    <p style="line-height:32pt; margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-indent:24pt; widows:0">
        <span style="font-family:方正仿宋_GBK; font-size:16pt">幼儿园建立健全园内申诉制度。分别成立园内家长申诉处理委员会和园内教师申诉处理委员会</span>
        <span style="font-family:方正仿宋_GBK; font-size:16pt">,</span>
        <span style="font-family:方正仿宋_GBK; font-size:16pt">明确受理家长和教师申诉的部门和程序。</span>
    </p>
    <p style="line-height:32pt; margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-indent:24pt; widows:0">
        <span style="font-family:方正仿宋_GBK; font-size:16pt">幼儿园建立健全人事争议调解机制。通过劳动</span>
        <span style="font-family:方正仿宋_GBK; font-size:16pt">（</span>
        <span style="font-family:方正仿宋_GBK; font-size:16pt">人事</span>
        <span style="font-family:方正仿宋_GBK; font-size:16pt">）</span>
        <span style="font-family:方正仿宋_GBK; font-size:16pt">争议调解委员会</span>
        <span style="font-family:方正仿宋_GBK; font-size:16pt">，</span>
        <span style="font-family:方正仿宋_GBK; font-size:16pt">就教职工与幼儿园的劳动</span>
        <span style="font-family:方正仿宋_GBK; font-size:16pt">(</span>
        <span style="font-family:方正仿宋_GBK; font-size:16pt">人事</span>
        <span style="font-family:方正仿宋_GBK; font-size:16pt">）</span>
        <span style="font-family:方正仿宋_GBK; font-size:16pt">争议进行调解；通过人事调解委员会</span>
        <span style="font-family:方正仿宋_GBK; font-size:16pt">，</span>
        <span style="font-family:方正仿宋_GBK; font-size:16pt">就幼儿、教职工、幼儿园间的各种纠纷进行调解。</span>
    </p>
    <p style="line-height:32pt; margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-indent:24pt; widows:0">
        <span style="font-family:方正仿宋_GBK; font-size:16pt">4.幼儿园还建立健全人事档案管理制度，全面负责幼儿园人力资源档案的收集、整理和归档，确保教职工的利益。</span>
    </p>
